    <item>
      <title>伊朗称“非敌对”船只可以通过霍尔木兹海峡</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/world/middleeast/iran-strait-of-hormuz-ships.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府表示，与以色列或美国没有关系的船只将被允许通过，但尚不清楚是否有任何船只会尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/world/middleeast/iran-strait-of-hormuz-ships.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 09:48:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人艾米莉·格雷戈里赢得佛罗里达州海湖庄园特别选举</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/florida-special-election-emily-gregory.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[艾米丽·格雷戈里在棕榈滩的胜利将民主党的浪潮带到了特朗普总统的后院，而一位工会领导人在争夺佛罗里达州副州长空出的州参议院席位的竞选中处于领先地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/florida-special-election-emily-gregory.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 07:48:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉瓜迪亚空难考验新港务局领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/nyregion/port-authority-laguardia-crash-firefighters.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯瑟琳·加西亚 (Kathryn Garcia) 从二月份开始领导该机构，她安慰了两名受伤的消防员，并处理了为纽约市服务的三个大型机场的延误问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/nyregion/port-authority-laguardia-crash-firefighters.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 02:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在拉瓜迪亚空难中丧生的加拿大航空飞行员都处于飞行生涯的早期</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/nyregion/air-canada-pilots-laguardia.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飞行员被确认为 30 岁的安东尼·福里斯特 (Antoine Forest) 和麦肯齐·冈瑟 (Mackenzie Gunther)。他们是纽约拉瓜迪亚机场飞机与消防车相撞事故中仅有的两人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/nyregion/air-canada-pilots-laguardia.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 01:25:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北卡罗来纳州参议员菲尔·伯杰正式输给萨姆·佩奇</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/berger-page-north-carolina-senate-gop.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲尔·伯杰拥有金钱、权力和特朗普总统的支持。但他的批评者们对他充满了不满，周二，他仅以 23 票之差落败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/berger-page-north-carolina-senate-gop.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 01:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院共和党人再次阻止未经授权停止伊朗战争的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/senate-iran-war-vote.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党人第三次未能提出一项决议，该决议将迫使军队撤出伊朗的敌对行动，除非国会批准进攻行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/senate-iran-war-vote.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 23:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党加紧努力达成国土安全部资助协议并结束停摆</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/senate-republicans-homeland-security-shutdown-ice.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普总统表示他不希望妥协的第二天，参议院共和党人向民主党人发送了一份计划，该计划将中断 ICE 执法资金并重新开放该部门的其他部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/senate-republicans-homeland-security-shutdown-ice.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 22:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森表示，他对将以色列与“种族隔离国家”相比较的言论感到遗憾</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/newsom-israel-apartheid-state.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长表示，他的意思是指以色列潜在的未来方向，而不是其当前的政策。 “我尊敬以色列国，”他说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/newsom-israel-apartheid-state.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:49:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称美国已向伊朗发送了结束中东战争的15点计划</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/world/middleeast/us-iran-peace-plan.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，这项 15 点计划是通过巴基斯坦交付的，巴基斯坦陆军参谋长已成为美国和伊朗之间的关键对话者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/world/middleeast/us-iran-peace-plan.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和共和党全国委员会倾向于达拉斯举行不寻常的 2026 年共和党中期大会</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/trump-republican-convention-dallas-midterm-elections.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政党通常每四年举行一次大会来提名总统候选人，但面对中期阻力，共和党希望今年举行一次大会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/24/us/politics/trump-republican-convention-dallas-midterm-elections.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 18:50:14 GMT</pubDate>
